{"tid":1692484,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【捷報】海港城第三季零售額跌35% 歷來最差","createTime":"2019-11-04T05:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T12:55:12.000Z","uid":236171,"like":171,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"5a46e60f8ae002448021a5da083c3e2563261a25","tid":1692484,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:59:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【護旗不力】海港城第三季零售額跌35% 歷來最差 (13:05)</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n文章日期：2019年11月4日<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">本港零售銷售貨值連跌8個月，最新9月報跌18.3%</span></strong>，銀河聯昌證券報告指出，九龍倉置業（1997）旗下海港城及時代廣場由於位處經常發生示威地區，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">海港城第三季零售銷售跌幅高達35%，時代廣場第三季零售銷售跌幅亦達30%</span></strong>﹔首三季方面，海港城零售銷售跌幅將達11.6%，而時代廣場則要跌11.8%，均差於該行預期。<br />\n<br />\n據銀河聯昌證券中港房地產研究主管鄭懷武表示，相信兩個商場全年的零售銷售亦有機會跌達15至20%，主要由於去年本港重要基建像港珠澳大橋及高鐵開通後，帶來的高基數效應，示威令到國內旅客減少，而海港城的旅客中至少60%至70%主要為內地客。<br />\n<br />\n該行指出，9月零售銷售貨值跌18.3%至299億元，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">主要是受到特別是中國旅客的訪港旅客跌34.2%影響，相信10月的零售數據或更差</span></strong>，主要由於愈趨激進的社會事件，以及去年因開通了高鐵、港珠澳大橋的影響，導致第四季零售銷售數據基數較高，而在黃金周首日已見內地旅客下降了六成。"},{"pid":"d41fe9c2cbb90f00658cdee125413596d324ecbc","tid":1692484,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:59:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f/article/20191104/s00002/1572844322319\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%2Farticle%2F20191104%2Fs00002%2F1572844322319&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWftHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=e1644222\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%2Farticle%2F20191104%2Fs00002%2F1572844322319&h=a268dd15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f/article/20191104/s00002/1572844322319</a>"},{"pid":"71c7444565aea98f6223fb6e1cb533c9283a1a16","tid":1692484,"uid":189157,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:00:15.000Z","msg":"不完美，可接受，要改進<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127c64459c0163f8d6c1923fe1c641cbd1345d92","tid":1692484,"uid":22675,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:00:21.000Z","msg":"35%咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />起碼要65%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516a03777aaca6afa49554142c82b3f53a5e56de","tid":1692484,"uid":8014,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:01:20.000Z","msg":"仲係跌咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n起馬跌夠8成先叫攬炒啦"},{"pid":"66838c4b6cfc6c8d4951d116f5166c44087831df","tid":1692484,"uid":331682,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:03:03.000Z","msg":"要跌到0"},{"pid":"87c91237fefc4d1dce8fdae1808e6241a5983e62","tid":1692484,"uid":236171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"127c64459c0163f8d6c1923fe1c641cbd1345d92","tid":1692484,"uid":22675,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:00:21.000Z","msg":"35%咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />起碼要65%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:03:03.000Z","msg":"一步一步嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee6af244dbd67d5069262db13788cc1327b87bd","tid":1692484,"uid":197121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:05:29.000Z","msg":"捷報<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81649a594741893e1087125bac1c300543a21e6a","tid":1692484,"uid":41423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:07:03.000Z","msg":"仍需努力"},{"pid":"5f6838ab0b4c0760318b1218cdafa8a98784fccc","tid":1692484,"uid":230104,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:07:1