n></strong>，主要由於愈趨激進的社會事件，以及去年因開通了高鐵、港珠澳大橋的影響，導致第四季零售銷售數據基數較高，而在黃金周首日已見內地旅客下降了六成。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:06:16.000Z","msg":"你同警察講"},{"pid":"f40b536bcc126294bd5c156141f9d0b79f0cb233","tid":1692484,"uid":133743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:07:42.000Z","msg":"抵撚死，而家揸旗嗰個係大劉以前條女"},{"pid":"7e19afad05916f829204056700153a1c39748785","tid":1692484,"uid":75556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f6838ab0b4c0760318b1218cdafa8a98784fccc","tid":1692484,"uid":230104,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:07:16.000Z","msg":"九龍倉吳光正好支持林鄭架，得償所願"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:07:49.000Z","msg":"包家家門不幸<br />\n<br />\n臨老晩節不保"},{"pid":"6d9e0bd3fcfa68c3b452d2339c0ab643576b8272","tid":1692484,"uid":64354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:08:16.000Z","msg":"姐係仲有7成可以跌"},{"pid":"e2d5c988131ec8ad0c228f9bd23ce2226ecc27bb","tid":1692484,"uid":289442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:12:10.000Z","msg":"唔夠50%唔合格<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8863603c265443137d3df25c58840d882f2b62f9","tid":1692484,"uid":119610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:13:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e1fc06a4ad8222cb26b1860cc321c7dd9da7ed","tid":1692484,"uid":273228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:18:30.000Z","msg":"一日廣東道仲係道就收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28b37475062592fd9bc1fc4d7ccf788ec3eb659","tid":1692484,"uid":273228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30e1fc06a4ad8222cb26b1860cc321c7dd9da7ed","tid":1692484,"uid":273228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019